TrapRL is a roguelike created for the 7DRL challenge of 2012.
It features gameplay based around traps, and a different health system.
The homepage is at: http://codingden.net
Keys:

  Arrow keys: Movement and navigation in inventory.
  I: open inventory.
  Q: Quit game, or close inventory
  E: Use item if in inventory, or pick up objects.
  F: Prepare to jump, next move propels you two tiles, and over/underneath some traps.
  .: Wait.

To change the font, edit traprl.cfg and change font1.png to font2.png, font3.png or font4.png.